title: Chocolate Mousse
directions: Put the entire packet of sugar-free pudding mix in a medium bowl, and add the whipping cream
With an electric mixer, whip on high for about one minute (until thick)
Divide into 8 even servings (not 4 like the box says)
Yield: 8 servings, each with: 22g Fat; 1g Protein; 2g carbohydrates
ingredients: 1 (1.4 oz) box sugar-free pudding mix (I used chocolate, any flavor works well)
